
sequenceDiagram
    participant JS as JetStream
    participant GI as graph-ingest
    participant ES as ENTITY_STATES
    participant GX as graph-index
    participant IX as Index Buckets

    JS->>GI: entity.sensor.temperature
    GI->>GI: Validate ID format
    GI->>GI: Infer hierarchy (optional)
    GI->>ES: PUT entity (CAS with version)
    Note over ES: KV watch triggers
    ES-->>GX: Watch notification
    GX->>GX: Extract triples
    GX->>IX: Update OUTGOING_INDEX
    GX->>IX: Update INCOMING_INDEX
    GX->>IX: Update PREDICATE_INDEX

